      <para id="para-00042">Step 3 — Hold a runoff election. In other words, hold a second round. Since we have a list of the voters’ preferences with the eliminated option removed, we will renumber the preferences as first, second,and third so that we keep the original order of preference. The result is that we will count the second-place vote of any voter whose first choice was eliminated.</para>
